      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. YANNICK (7) missed the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 435m at Sale in 24.37. Has the ability and expected to go close again. DR. ERICA (3) was quickly into stride and burnt early from out wide where she gave a sight, finishing second (24.50) and beaten 1.3 lengths over 435m at Sale. Expecting another good run. DAINTREE DAMAGE (1) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing sixth (23.14) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Can measure up this time. IDYLLIC JAMES (8) was out of placings last time (28.72) at Bendigo in a Grade 5, finishing eighth and beaten 12 lengths. Has already won four times from this draw.",
